highlights.text: “FRI(END)S” by V is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Hong Kong, up 90 spots at #82.
Anson Lo 盧瀚霆 has the most spots on Top Songs Hong Kong. “Lemonade” is the highest at #5.
“反對無效” by MC 張天賦 has been on Top Songs Hong Kong the longest, at 1579 days straight.
“Blink (feat. TZUYU)” by Corbyn Besson and TZUYU is the highest new entry on Top Songs Hong Kong at #198.
